These things won’t cost you a penny, but she will love it for sure- 
🌷 . Give her a massage- 
Trust me, this is the best thing you can give your mother to relax. She is already fed up, tired and muscle-tensed because of all the housework. A nice therapeutic massage with a light music on or chit chat session with you can cheer her up. 
🌷. Cook for her- 
Lessen her burden of cooking and cleaning by doing the work for her. She has a 24X7 duty- just ask her to take a day off! 
🌷. Clean up the space- 
The tidy space, everything on its place will give her so much happiness, especially if she hasn’t done it. 
🌷. Give her some time- 
She will for sure love spending time with her younger version because these days nobody has enough time to say these simple words - Maa I Love You ❤️ 
…. And on top of that, if you can give her some clothes, bags, accessories, footwear or makeup as a gift- this will be a cherry on cake! 🍰 🌷
.
.PS-: This video is from my London trip 😍😙
